<br>
If you didn't take the time to group and make friends pre-50 then you've kind of screwed yourself post-50. I know I did not have much trouble finding groups because I made quite a few friends as I leveled up which always makes it easier.<br>
<br>
Makes friends when you are lower level by grouping and it will pay dividends at higher levels. <p>Natharius Bladestorm<br>
